They decided to stop a car to perform the route control. The driver did not follow the instructions, suddenly increased the speed and tried to escape the control.
The police began the persecution until the car stopped at the edge of the road after a few kilometres. At that moment the drivers got out of the car to escape over a country road into a forest area.
